[au:]使你很难有破坏性的想法.\n
[02:48.97]It is only someone looking on from outsi- de that can inject the dangerous thoughts.\n
[au:]只有外部的旁观者才能灌输危险的思想.\n
[02:56.11]I do not doubt that it would be possible to inject ideas into the modern world,\n
