[03:24.82]of supplying suffcient details to enable the thing to be constructed.\n
[au:]且向它提供制造核弹的细节,影响将有多大.\n
[03:30.15]20 or 30 pages of information,\n
[au:]如果把二三十页的情报,\n
[03:33.36]handed to any of the major world powers around the year 1925,\n
[au:]交给1925年前后的任何一个世界强国,\n
[03:38.86]would have been sufficient to change the course of world history.\n
[au:]就足以改变世界历史的进程.\n
[03:42.82]It is a strange thought,but I believe a correct one,\n
